{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"abcd26e7fa","title":"给徐明清的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"18b0cdac65","index":0,"year":1946,"month":4,"day":14,"articleId":"abcd26e7fa"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji21","name":"毛泽东全集第21卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji21.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji21":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"b66c2c2cdb","type":"paragraph","text":"给徐明清的信”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji21","articleId":"abcd26e7fa"},{"id":"b56f197a40","type":"paragraph","text":"（1946年4月14日）明清同志你的信我们都看了，甚为感动。观润同志的病情如此，当然使你难过到这种程度：但是一种事实到了面前，如果是无可如何时再急再痛也无益，只好承认事实，而客观地对待之。何况观澜的病不一定是你所说的那样，不一定不能救…请你代我们问候观同志。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji21","articleId":"abcd26e7fa"},{"id":"a14c537bd2","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji21","articleId":"abcd26e7fa"},{"id":"14b488b7c6","type":"paragraph","text":"四月十四日[1]当时王观澜病重，生命危在旦夕。王观润的妻子徐明清含着泪水，给毛泽东写了一封充满您伤情绪的信。此时，为了应对国民党全面内战的署，毛泽东的工作相当繁位，但接到徐明清的信后，他还是很快索笔写了端","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji21","articleId":"abcd26e7fa"}],"page":{"id":"5957dc08fd","publicationId":"maoquanji21","articleId":"abcd26e7fa","start":244,"end":244}}}},"__N_SSG":true}